<div class="question1"  style="display:none;">
<p class="question">
<h2><b><span style="color:red;">Test 2.1</span></b></h2>
 The system 
$\displaystyle
\frac{d^2y}{dt^2}+3t\frac{dy}{dt}+y(t)=x(t)
$ is:
  
    <ul class="answers">
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q1ai"/><input type="radio" name="q1" value="a" id="q1a"><label for="q1a">Linear                           </label><br>       
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q1bi"/><input type="radio" name="q1" value="b" id="q1b"><label for="q1b">Time-invariant                   </label><br>          
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q1ci"/><input type="radio" name="q1" value="c" id="q1c"><label for="q1c">Linear time-invariant            </label><br>        
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q1di"/><input type="radio" name="q1" value="d" id="q1d"><label for="q1d">Neither linear nor time-invariant</label><br>
    </ul>
    
<script>
  document.getElementById('q1a').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('q1b').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('q1c').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('q1d').checked = false;
answer_value[1] = "a";
</script>
<div id="question1_answer" style="display:none;">
<span style="color:red;">Solution:</span><br> The system is not time-invariant
due to the time-varying coefficient $(3t)$.
</div>
<br>
</div>






<div class="question2"  style="display:none;">
<p class="question">
<h2><b><span style="color:red;">Test 2.2</span></b></h2>
The system 
$\displaystyle
\frac{d^2y}{dt^2}+3\frac{dy}{dt}+y(t)=x(t)
$ is:
  
    <ul class="answers">
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q2ai"/><input type="radio" name="q2" value="a" id="q2a"><label for="q2a">Linear                           </label><br>       
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q2bi"/><input type="radio" name="q2" value="b" id="q2b"><label for="q2b">Time-invariant                   </label><br>          
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q2ci"/><input type="radio" name="q2" value="c" id="q2c"><label for="q2c">Linear time-invariant            </label><br>        
<img src="blank.png" width="15" id="q2di"/><input type="radio" name="q2" value="d" id="q2d"><label for="q2d">Neither linear nor time-invariant</label><br>
    </ul>
    
<script>
  document.getElementById('q2a').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('q2b').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('q2c').checked = false;
  document.getElementById('q2d').checked = false;
answer_value[2] = "c";
</script>
<div id="question2_answer" style="display:none;">
<span style="color:red;">Solution:</span><br>This is a linear
constant-coefficient differential equation (LCCDE), so the system is
LTI.
</div>
<br>
</div>






<div class="question3"  style="display:none;">
