<div id="question17_answer" style="display:none;">
<span style="color:red;">Solution:</span><br>
$\displaystyle {\bf H} (\omega) = \frac{1}{j\omega+3}, $<br> 
$\displaystyle {\bf H}(3) = \frac{1}{3+j3}=\frac{1}{3\sqrt{2}}e^{-j45^\circ },$<br>
so<br>
$\displaystyle
\frac{3\sqrt{2}}{3\sqrt{2}}\cos(3t-45^\circ )=\cos(3t-45^\circ).
$
</div>
